# Organisation Control Responsible Person Status Change Code

## identifier
de13756

## type
string

## definition
This indicates the status of the responsible person.

## guidance
The valid enumerated values are:  
Changed = if any information about an existing responsible person has changed.  
Unchanged = if all information about an existing responsible person remains unchanged.  
No longer acting as a responsible person = if the existing responsible person is no longer a responsible person.

## codes
| Name                                     |
| ---------------------------------------- |
| Changed                                  |
| No longer acting as a responsible person |
| Unchanged                                |

## syntax
### xbrl
- name=OrganisationControl.ResponsiblePersonStatusChange.Code
- classification=py/pyde/pyde.02.18
- period=duration
